OL,4,CAfghan women to have rights within
OL,5,CIslamic law, Taliban say
OL,6, The rights of women in Afghanistan will
OL,7, be respected "within the framework of
OL,8, Islamic law", the Taliban say.
OL,10,FIn the group's first news conference
OL,11,Fsince taking control of the country on
OL,12,FSunday, a spokesman said women would be
OL,13,Ffree to work but gave little detail
OL,14,Fabout other rules and restrictions.
OL,16,FZabihullah Mujahid repeated that all
OL,17,FAfghans must live "within the framework
OL,18,Fof Islam".
OL,20,FRights groups fear women's freedoms
OL,21,Fcould be eroded under the Taliban.
